{"tid":818772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【颱風百科】膠紙貼窗防風？　美國家氣象機構：浪費時間及膠紙","createTime":"2018-09-14T10:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T23:21:08.000Z","uid":202698,"like":196,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"5d6c68ef3f48992c62d0854c11ca09e2ac60ce6e","tid":818772,"uid":202698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/14/182911_0a383badfd3a17c317d4610e2bef076e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F14%2F182911_0a383badfd3a17c317d4610e2bef076e.jpg&h=141ae489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人遇上颱風時，均會在窗戶上貼上膠紙，以免玻璃窗被強風吹至爆裂。<span style=\"color: red;\">但亦有指在窗戶貼膠紙無甚作用，美國國家海洋及大氣管理局更直指此舉浪費時間及膠紙。</span>究竟打風天應否在窗上貼膠紙？貼上膠紙又有何作用？<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》向理工大學前機械工程學系工程師盧覺強求證，他指在窗上貼膠紙，亦非完全無用<br />\n<br />\n盧覺強指出，市民在玻璃窗上以「交叉」或「格仔」形式貼上膠紙，旨在減少玻璃震盪，「傍住塊玻璃」。與此同時，窗戶貼上膠紙亦可在玻璃碎裂時，保持玻璃碎片呈大塊狀，<span style=\"color: red;\">「少啲機會碎哂跌落街」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美國國家海洋及大氣管理局</span>（National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration, NOAA）在其網頁中謬誤一欄，解釋市民是否應在窗戶貼膠紙，<span style=\"color: red;\">直指「It is a waste of effort, time, and tape」（這是浪費力氣、時間及膠紙），認為此舉只會稍稍強化玻璃抵禦強風壓力，</span>但當玻璃窗要碎裂時，也未能提供保護作用。該局又呼籲，若市民在窗上貼膠紙，更應花時間用防風閘遮閉窗戶。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/14/183101_5f6d01cb61065e8b1d59e749f0958157.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F14%2F183101_5f6d01cb61065e8b1d59e749f0958157.jpg&h=7df99521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實香港天文台在其網頁中，呼籲市民在八號烈風或暴風信號生效時，「當風的大玻璃窗應加貼膠紙，減少玻璃破裂時所引致的損傷」，但並無提及，膠紙可防止玻璃被強風吹裂。天文台亦提醒，市民應遠離當風門窗，並應提早決定，當窗隻被強風吹裂時，哪個房間可作棲身之用。"},{"pid":"6db9dd2a53256231f7915380220efca37293331c","tid":818772,"uid":182499,"like":403,"dislike":3,"score":400,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:36:22.000Z","msg":"好多商場玻璃本身貼咗隔熱膜再貼膠紙係多餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea3e13ce85486853818c35e84a1e606f75c2f95","tid":818772,"uid":66242,"like":1015,"dislike":4,"score":1011,"quote":{"pid":"6db9dd2a53256231f7915380220efca37293331c","tid":818772,"uid":182499,"like":403,"dislike":3,"score":400,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:36:22.000Z","msg":"好多商場玻璃本身貼咗隔熱膜再貼膠紙係多餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:50:53.000Z","msg":"前線未必知<br />\n上面有柯打就做<br />\n出事唔使上身<br />\n打份工唔是做科學主任<br />\n香港奴工唔要求帶腦番工"},{"pid":"42dcff1d1dcbec64a12ca8339eb88c2cbd00f83c","tid":818772,"uid":154702,"like":822,"dislike":14,"score":808,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"你都戇鳩鳩，美國啲平房一吹就成間屋吹走梗係唔使癡膠紙<br />\n香港石屎森林居住環境密集，有機會減低損傷嘅都有必要做"},{"pid":"d3dc3969376704dfdfd90ab18fc5c7f8fe508fee","tid":818772,"uid":73443,"like":67,"dislike":2,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:54:53.000Z","msg":"舊個d一碎會一大片<br />\n依家好似多數碎d同會痴住咁碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b29c42c64b63ae49421c7e5daeb55f65344ff2","tid":818772,"uid":76776,"like":80,"dislike":1,"score":79,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:55:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6599a9487bb682daecede3f7215226719abc2ef8","tid":818772,"uid":4493,"like":212,"dislike":9,"score":203,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:55:05.000Z","msg":"美國根本好少建築類似香港<br />\n邊度有得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbc33c4f3915f5d88e5d5b7263344a8fa6fb397","tid":818772,"uid":112606,"like":167,"dislike":9,"score":158,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:55:06.000Z","msg":"美國個套點apply 落香港到呀<br />\n防風板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"