0.000Z","msg":"台灣就算平時有d野on99<br />\n都起碼會做實驗試<br />\n香港就成班盲毛同玩神打一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.abri.gov.tw/tw/periodical/show/88/1676\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.abri.gov.tw%2Ftw%2Fperiodical%2Fshow%2F88%2F1676&d=3yIU3YvVbR2hif99R5thy0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a69bff4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.abri.gov.tw/tw/periodical/show/88/1676</a>"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T15:47:08.000Z","msg":"經過試驗，可以發現以下幾項重點：<br />\n<br />\n5mm普通玻璃在本次試驗中受強大風壓而破裂，同時發現無貼膠帶的抗風壓值較優於各種不同膠帶貼法的情形（接近5,000Pa），即便是貼了不同形式的膠帶或全部貼滿的狀態下，並沒有增加窗扇的抗風壓能力，過程也發現膠帶的功用比較傾向於減少玻璃破碎時的飛濺。另外，在5mm強化玻璃抗風對照試驗過程中，量測壓力已接近10,000Pa時，玻璃仍然沒有破裂，惟窗扇本身的框架斷裂變形導致無法持續加壓而停止試驗。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T21:07:35.000Z","msg":"其實普通屋企係用強化玻璃定普通玻璃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3837c7049c8c2d799e664c64bad3ce3490ae0b","tid":818772,"uid":105166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdbc6e0c9919af6c7b0b1f0065d22750d7536166","tid":818772,"uid":113326,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"1f34a58af422d28719692dc911cdde7e4f6d21b1","tid":818772,"uid":26770,"like":53,"dislike":4,"score":49,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T11:26:50.000Z","msg":"台灣就算平時有d野on99<br />\n都起碼會做實驗試<br />\n香港就成班盲毛同玩神打一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.abri.gov.tw/tw/periodical/show/88/1676\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.abri.gov.tw%2Ftw%2Fperiodical%2Fshow%2F88%2F1676&d=3yIU3YvVbR2hif99R5thy0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a69bff4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.abri.gov.tw/tw/periodical/show/88/1676</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T17:22:33.000Z","msg":"印象中, 學是學非實驗過<br />\n痴膠紙係有用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T21:09:20.000Z","msg":"有用係咩位先"},{"pid":"0e32145d2276110148bcaa40882d49f4728b0d78","tid":818772,"uid":64969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T21:1